kgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條撚樣柒撚完又要死出黎轉軑攞彩驚撚死冇人知佢做過正義之士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主今鋪真係要支持，揭穿班假仁假義既偽君子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c715ae7afeb41aa9f1de8c7b2c05c6c908df5b2","tid":89631,"uid":54918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你仲以為索尼NEX6不嬲高質開今鋪睇撚錯佢</blockquote><br />\n呢條友仲柒過backup佬,一開頭屌達哥最用力係佢,之後見唔對路又變翻支持達哥<br />\n噁心到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牆頭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條撚樣柒撚完又要死出黎轉軑攞彩驚撚死冇人知佢做過正義之士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主今鋪真係要支持，揭穿班假仁假義既偽君子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食撚屎啦垃圾索尼NEX6<br />\n成撚日講到自己好撚有道理咁<br />\n原來都係一隻狗黎"},{"pid":"f80ed8c3f9fec2c0e2778004358635dbf94cc86c","tid":89631,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澄清返我比人cap留言張cap圖留言來源，呢幾條留言來源都係quote  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tYBl9jhuDvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtYBl9jhuDvo&d=GUU7mf6OPVfDQHBw2W5ePJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7a1071e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tYBl9jhuDvo</a><br />\n<br />\nbackup佬琴日話問過達哥但達哥無覆。而佢都自動停左做backup。<br />\no係度我希望達哥認真覆一覆佢(甚至係其他精華兄弟)。如果你真係唔鍾意,介意佢地影響你收入或者乜乜物物都好,同佢地禮貌講聲,所有野你自己做返,我諗係最好既結果。但如果連覆都唔覆,甚至想怪咁多位backup同精華兄弟,我會對你好失望...﻿<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;留言位人兄已經刪除留言</span><br />\n<br />\n早排先係fifa度暗示過youtube有人偷片揾食唔問佢，而家達太祖立刻宣示主權！！ 不過冇chatroom版我都係會睇番backup佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW271ix5TNtFFWgVrMW1DUFwe8SitqiNuT3cw8uQnYuj1?filename=1cQtdLa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cQtdLa.png&h=b80d6cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次達哥玩人中，兄弟都唔洗睇chatroom，全部都係劇透，嗌skip劇情，好慢好悶呢啲comment﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/235611_56ddc46eae1a162892c6a8c490cfb3a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F235611_56ddc46eae1a162892c6a8c490cfb3a0.png&h=a26ed78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔可以咁講, 只係一開始undergrounddv自己唔放上youtube, youtube佬只係幫大家放上另一個渠道加chatroom俾大家重溫, 大膽d講, 呢幾年無左backup佬, 會有咁多人睇達哥？backup佬無功都有勞, 同埋宣示主權既概念唔係好岩, 達哥somehow都係攞人地隻game搵食, 開發商大可以用同一個道理唔俾達哥用佢隻game, 大家彼此留個空間比較好, 支持backup佬繼續雙版本backup~﻿<br />\n<br />\ntwitch download唔到, Youtube可以, download定出街唁洗數據都睇到﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdv22nAGd97naSVhrXkusdqMyX6d9bF8C6JRCbTM1JWZe?filename=548o32z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F548o32z.png&h=af0c6f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ninclude埋chatroom先會睇呢邊﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT8CFnDossHw5zoxV5Y27rBgndZnYEtw8tsXxj9qCnkak?filename=WSUdDd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSUdDd0.png&h=89636a8d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/89780/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F89780%2Fpage%2F1&d=GUU7mf6OPVfDQHBw2W5ePJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=fd885850\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/89780/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1177ccbb992d179808a4f2197f1dbcc1e45062c4","tid":89631,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班柒頭未知件事係點就已經發表偉論,真係柒到唔敢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成篇長文 一夜變廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87b10eacb37c75de049893d9547b7ed986f5388","tid":89631,"uid":56277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl